{"tid":1288601,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"千奇唔好18區「同時」遊行！","createTime":"2019-07-05T16:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T15:34:05.000Z","uid":257767,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e29f7329276811dcbfd343c16a1afb8cfe89b735","tid":1288601,"uid":257767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"分18區逐次搞可以，但千奇唔好同時搞！<br />\n<br />\n同時搞遊行，理論上每區人數分薄左，人數必定少<br />\n<br />\n1)變相免費幫政府統計，每區大概有咩／幾多人支持，增加政府big data。<br />\n<br />\n2) 由於人數較少，警察監控同搵人亦較容易，增加每人承受既風險。"},{"pid":"1786a5be7123e52d32bf3ce4a005e812feb2970a","tid":1288601,"uid":257767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"3)假設你朋友先係政府目標，而你又係中學生，咁好大機會你朋友同樣住係該區。警察可以透過拘捕你，而試圖打聽你朋友既下落。"},{"pid":"3c1a6f0d72707c24ef511577e4de61dc14968acd","tid":1288601,"uid":257767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"4)同時遊行完，基本上又要諗新idea。相反，如果分18區，18日咁遊行，可以拖長民氣，繼續做落去。"},{"pid":"6b7cccf4f379b4682d74ec031d765f3b87dd4491","tid":1288601,"uid":6549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"唔會批"},{"pid":"78ade44b1be78938c1bb60d07cda84b4edaf44b2","tid":1288601,"uid":236302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"5bc355542a219c64ec4938f81a8c4d1c6974cdad","tid":1288601,"uid":257767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfcd8c0438c05fc2f946617fc1a5cf7aee70587","tid":1288601,"uid":257767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\